III. How we share your data
We are committed to maintaining your trust, and
we do not sell personal data to third parties
, we want you to understand when and with whom we may share the data we collect for business purposes.
Service Providers and Business Partners
We share the categories of normal personal data listed above with service providers and business partners to help us perform business operations and for business purposes, including research, payment processing and transaction fulfillment, database maintenance, administering contests and special offers, technology services, deliveries, email deployment, advertising, analytics, measurement, data storage and hosting, disaster recovery, search engine optimization, marketing, and data processing.
Within Our Corporate Group
We may share your personal data with a parent, subsidiary, or other affiliate of our corporate group for better service.
For Legal Reasons
We will cooperate with all third parties to enforce their intellectual property or other rights
and
we
will also cooperate with law enforcement enquiries from within your country of residence. So
we may disclose your data to respond to subpoenas, court orders, legal process, law enforcement requests, legal claims, or government inquiries, and to protect and defend the rights, interests, safety, and security of Mika, the Platform, our affiliates, users, or the public
believe that disclosure
We may also share your data to enforce any terms applicable to the Platform, to exercise or defend any legal claims, and comply with any applicable law in our discretion.
With Your Consent
We may share data for other purposes pursuant to your explicit consent or with your further direction.
To ensure you get to meet as many people as possible on Mika, other users will have chance to check your data you post on Profile.
If you choose to engage in public activities on the Platform, you should be cautious to disclose personal data while engaging. We are not responsible for the data you choose to submit.
Any data you choose to provide should reflect how much you want other Mika users to know about you. And
